test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (1 == 3)
 +  where 1 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ab25ba6edc0>([-30])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7ab25ba6edc0> = [[1, -30, 1, -30, 1, -30], [1, -30, 1, -30, 1, -30], [-30, 1, -30, 1, -30], [-30, 1, -30, 1, -30], [1, -30, 1, -30], [1, -30, 1, -30], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -656100000000 == -30
 +  where -656100000000 = <built-in function prod>([-2, -3, -5, -6, -10, -15, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
